{"tid":1360090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[727] 和理非要相信勇武派   「不分化」唔好可以咁兒戲","createTime":"2019-07-24T09:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:55:45.000Z","uid":89160,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd09e1630b57a99e2fb534e7b17b8691d9c8b4e","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:28:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我絕對唔會相信現場既勇武派會無差別攻擊平民，我自己有眼見既，都已經成個月啦，大家都仲唔信任對方？</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nd和理非一聽到「黑社會」、「解放軍」呢d keywords 又開始驚，打壓勇武，唔記得求同存異，唔記得左五大訴求之外，仲有<strong><ins>四大原則</ins></strong>：「不割席、不分化、不篤魁、兄弟爬山」。<br />\n<br />\n的確係有人盲動，有爭拗，從來現場都可以平衡，<strong><ins>「相信現場」</ins></strong>就係呢一個月最大既得著，現場唔係完美，現場唔後無敵，但比網上可信得多。<br />\n<br />\n香港已經唔存在一個 100% legal and risk free 既抗爭，甚至唔係抗爭都會被波及，元朗事件本身就最佳例證。面對真正既「暴力」唔可以逃避、退讓，無論係和理非定勇武都唔應該再退縮，怕左d黑社會，唔好畀元朗成為黑社會既「租界」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>727 要多人，多一個人，多一分安全，各自努力</ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港  時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"33512e6d1427e7f79ffe00c6da44ffef4ff2ab2b","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4524245dc525cfe45c0b9239030b49398d551945","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadd96f9e9f0542fdc2906563b4e4026df61a185","tid":1360090,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9744ef6f552ee7c725ad3704b1f1adc07eff1fe2","tid":1360090,"uid":266098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:35:48.000Z","msg":"相信彼此<br />\n一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6c63b7aacb849f3438b59b9f109bc9796f7e61","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78030ac97498af28844c5e151abbd58925b7fb3","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5f4f9ee449ded8d33dad2b80b88a94c215f1dc","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5118cdfef81767db95b42629f68ec0ad3c014e91","tid":1360090,"uid":176016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"絕對相信勇武派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個班垃圾黑社會無差別咁打 成日吹到幾有義氣唔會蝦老弱婦孺 食屎啦<br />\n唔好用佢地同我地勇武比呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"cf66f87ee7ee93452fe84adedc28d0798da18d73","tid":1360090,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5118cdfef81767db95b42629f68ec0ad3c014e91","tid":1360090,"uid":176016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"絕對相信勇武派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個班垃圾黑社會無差別咁打 成日吹到幾有義氣唔會蝦老弱婦孺 食屎啦<br />\n唔好用佢地同我地勇武比呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n絕不分化 不割蓆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3c91be9129a3c946e967c4fbf5ed773c25f701","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50910ec2da1540a9369cd026025bc03d4db0faa3","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T18:35:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>我重申多次，<ins>勇武派從6月9號夜晚開始，都冇走去傷害平民</ins>，要破壞太古廣場、新城市d鋪早就爆晒。<br />\n<br />\n不分化唔係面和心不和，表面唔割暗地打壓，我真係相信佢地，甚至願意共同承擔壓力，<ins>而唔係假設勇武會失控</ins>。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"6203691110b2517f317e8a5dc6799fb8b82df82c","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c30dd24eafab22db4abb12823e2d46b6ecb30f1","tid":1360090,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:22:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>7.27入元朗踩場</strong><br />\n點樣先係將踩場發揮到<strong>極緻</strong>？就係入到人地頭，佢最想發生嘅事發生唔到，最唔想發生嘅事發生左。<br />\n<br />\n元朗啲黑社會最想就係打鳩啲黑衫示威者，要黑衫示威者打直入打橫出。對佢地最大嘅侮辱就係幾萬個黑衫示威者入去元朗佢地地頭周圍行，跟住咩事都無敢行返去元朗。<br />\n<br />\n同佢地打，我地實有人傷，正正係佢地想發生嘅事&mdash;&mdash;黑衫示威者入得元朗就無得預咩事都無敢返出去。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我地幾萬人着黑衫入元朗，完膚無傷敢行返出元朗，就係對元朗黑社會最大嘅嘲諷。</strong>"},{"pid":"9f9bafa483b165e783e9ab375d86adf981208b12","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:29:53.000Z","msg":"成日強調「燒村」、「拆祠堂」既聲音，其實係和理非佔多數，咁係誇大d 9upper 既意見，而無視現場真正既勇武者，甚至係變相幫助政府誇大風險。"},{"pid":"5f04ac74096cd1943ca6fc4b7d228e130ec19d88","tid":1360090,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bede1835933bf378122c180366cbb385be012238","tid":1360090,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2806a4324efd728a66b023e91c1b62ef0fa6e0e2","tid":1360090,"uid":10503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"我相信前線嘅智慧<br />\n佢地比你想像中更聰明"},{"pid":"6d6f16383fa8446ac0928c4ac1334a6aa68b55c0","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2806a4324efd728a66b023e91c1b62ef0fa6e0e2","tid":1360090,"uid":10503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:32:36.000Z","msg":"我相信前線嘅智慧<br />\n佢地比你想像中更聰明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:36:04.000Z","msg":"根本就係<br />\n仲記唔記 69 之前夠勁多 post 都話「唔好掉氣油彈」，事實證明冇根據<br />\n唔信現場，就去誇大網上 9upper ，係最錯既決定"},{"pid":"72254497669388abd8a1b76d4bb0d7c584c13c8b","tid":1360090,"uid":60408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"支持，不分化不割席<br />\n約定大家27/7 元朗"},{"pid":"30872448c64b106bc973201f5aa0151f316947fb","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cfad17d22e694d4c85058dbce843a6f055f5b2","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3945312b57d262efcd50937f263c496c991164c6","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4944c21f3fbd5519e8c5de7fbe593ad15e944a35","tid":1360090,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e57d9bacaacaf0a5b919e6f9f3f52321830c4c","tid":1360090,"uid":276208,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:56:02.000Z","msg":"借位一用<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請幫推到鄉民見到，希望聽日可以相安無事</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">誠懇請鄉民今次真係要<ins>阻止任何可疑人士（包括疑似示威者）入村</ins>，唔係又引起誤會／衝突就唔好啦~~ </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[投訴懶人包] 反對套丁及冒充原居民 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369127</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">齊上齊落，支持五大訴求<br />\n支持圍村去黑，還我平靜鄉郊<br />\n反恐反黑，由投訴撚做起</span></em>"}]}